Titolo: Blade Dancer: Lineage of Light

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: Blade Dancer: Lineage of Light, released in Japan as Blade Dancer: Thousand-Year Promise (ブレイドダンサー 千年の約束, Bureido Dansā Sennen no Yakusoku), is a video game made exclusively for the PlayStation Portable. It is a turn-based role-playing video game in which players take on the role of the boy Lance who must save the world with the help of his friends.